      "role": "user",
      "content": "that sounds okay, but saying \"unauthorized access\" might make people think hackers actually got in, even if we say we're proactive. if the press asks point blank \"was this a misconfiguration error or a security failure?\", how do we answer that without admitting we messed up the S3 settings? we really need to avoid that word \"misconfiguration\".",
